{{Quote|We are here&hellip;The fourth planet of this detached system at the edge of Granita Clusta.|Commander Willard|<ref name="TAS">''[[Star Wars: The Annotated Screenplays]]''</ref>}}
The '''Granita Clusta''' contained the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]].

==Behind the scenes==
According to ''[[Star Wars: The Annotated Screenplays]]'', the first draft of [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']] placed [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]] in the Granita Clusta.

